			<div class='-mx-3 flex flex-wrap items-center'>
				<div class='w-full max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-3 lg:w-6/12'>
					<div class='block-style-four wow fadeInLeft mb-17.5 lg:mb-0 2xl:ml-6 2xl:pr-12'>
						<div class='title-style-six'>
							<h2 class='font-Recoleta text-4xl font-normal text-black lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl'>
								What you'll receive (and why teams keep coming back)
							</h2>
						</div>
						<!-- /.title-style-ten -->
						<p class='mb-0 pt-2.5 pb-5 text-black lg:text-xl/7.5 2xl:pt-5 2xl:pb-7.5'>
							We turn your designs into production-ready Tailwind CSS, written to be easy to maintain, extend, and ship.
						</p>
						<ul class='mb-0 list-item list-none pl-0'>
							<li
								class='relative mb-5 pl-10 text-black before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:content-[url(../images/icon/icon_93.svg)] lg:text-lg/7.5'>
								Minimal custom CSS. Design tokens, spacing, and colors live in the Tailwind @theme where they belong.
							</li>
							<li
								class='relative mb-5 pl-10 text-black before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:content-[url(../images/icon/icon_93.svg)] lg:text-lg/7.5'>
								Hand-crafted HTML that matches your design exactly and works across all modern browsers and devices
								(Chrome, Safari, Firefox, iOS Safari, Chrome Android)
							</li>
							<li
								class='relative mb-5 pl-10 text-black before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:content-[url(../images/icon/icon_93.svg)] lg:text-lg/7.5'>
								A ready-to-run project with all files included. Install dependencies and run locally with a single
								command.
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class='ml-auto w-full max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-3 lg:w-6/12 2xl:w-5/12'>
					<div class='-mx-3 flex flex-wrap items-end'>
						<div class='wow fadeInUp w-full max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-3 sm:w-4/12 md:w-5/12'>
							<img
								src='images/lazy.svg'
								data-src='images/shape/shape_136.svg'
								alt=''
								class='lazy-img hidden sm:inline-block'
							/>
						</div>
						<div class='wow fadeInDown w-full max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-3 sm:w-8/12 md:w-7/12'>
							<div
								class='block-wrapper block-one rounded-[45px_0_45px_0] border-[1.5px] border-solid border-[#FFAE10] bg-[#FFF3C9] pt-8.75 pr-3.75 pb-5 pl-3.75 sm:pb-7.5 sm:pl-8.75'>
								<h3
									class='mb-3.5 text-[26px]/[1.16em] xl:text-4xl xl:leading-10'
									style='color:#FFAE10;'>
									Friendly
								</h3>
								<p class='text-base/7.5 text-black/70 xl:text-lg/[29px]'>
									You'll work directly with us. Clear communication, fast replies, no hand-offs or middlemen.
								</p>
							</div>
							<!-- /.block-wrapper -->
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class='-mx-3 flex flex-wrap 2xl:-mx-6'>
						<div class='wow fadeInDown w-full max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-5 sm:w-7/12 xl:w-6/12'>
							<div
								class='block-wrapper block-two relative mt-7.5 rounded-[45px_0_45px_0] border-[1.5px] border-solid border-[#9650EF] bg-[rgba(162,91,251,0.2)] pt-5 pr-3.75 pb-5 pl-3.75 sm:pt-10 sm:pr-5 sm:pl-7.5 md:mt-12.5'>
								<h3
									class='mb-3.5 text-[26px]/[1.16em] xl:text-4xl xl:leading-10'
									style='color:#9650EF;'>
									Proven
								</h3>
								<p class='text-base/7.5 text-black/70 xl:text-lg/[29px]'>
									100+ projects delivered for agencies and product teams who care about clean, reusable front-end code.
								</p>
								<img
									src='images/lazy.svg'
									data-src='images/shape/shape_138.svg'
									alt=''
									class='lazy-img shapes shape-one absolute -bottom-11.25 -left-11.25 -z-1'
								/>
							</div>
							<!-- /.block-wrapper -->
						</div>
						<div class='wow fadeInUp w-full max-w-full flex-[0_0_auto] px-5 sm:w-5/12 xl:w-6/12'>
							<div
								class='block-wrapper block-three mt-7.5 rounded-[0_30px_0_30px] border-[1.5px] border-solid border-[#00BDE5] bg-[rgba(0,209,255,0.2)] pt-8.75 pr-3.75 pb-5 pl-3.75 sm:pt-5.5 sm:pb-3.75 sm:pl-7.5 md:mt-12.5'>
								<h3
									class='mb-3.5 text-[26px]/[1.16em] xl:text-4xl xl:leading-10'
									style='color:#00BDE6;'>
									Quality
								</h3>
								<p class='text-base/7.5 text-black/70 xl:text-lg/[29px]'>
									Well-structured markup, sensible class composition, and thoughtful components built to last.
								</p>
							</div>
							<!-- /.block-wrapper -->
							<img
								src='images/lazy.svg'
								data-src='images/shape/shape_137.svg'
								alt=''
								class='lazy-img mx-auto mt-7.5 hidden sm:inline-block'
							/>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
